{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_MaulerTorpedoWave}}
'''A_MaulerTorpedoWave'''<br />
(no parameters)

Spawns 80 {{class|MaulerTorpedoWave|Torpedo Wave}} projectiles at the center of the calling actor. Each of these new projectiles have the same Master and Target as the calling actor, and their angles are set so they are fired in a 360-degree ring.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|MaulerTorpedo}} and derived classes.

